query:
SELECT 'HOTEL' as type, id, name FROM hotels 
UNION ALL 
SELECT 'DOC' as type, id, name FROM documents WHERE (category='other' OR category='booking') AND (fileUrl LIKE '%.jpg' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.jpeg' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.png' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.webp' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.JPG' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.PNG')
ORDER BY type, name;
